In the Matter of Henrietta Austin, Petitioner, v Joseph D’Elia, as Commissioner of Nassau County Department of Social Services, et al., Respondents.

— Determination of the respondent State Commissioner of Social Services, dated November 3, 1980 and made after a statutory fair hearing, *952confirmed and proceeding dismissed on the merits, without costs or disbursements. No opinion. Thompson, J. P., Brown, Rubin and Boyers, JJ., concur.
